[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      160[0m:[38;5;10m[49m #### 🟡 NET-1: VPC Endpoint List Is Incomplete for the Stated Architecture
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      161[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      162[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Finding:** The Prerequisites table states "Lambda in VPC with endpoints for S3, DynamoDB, SageMaker Runtime, Kinesis, and CloudWatch Logs." This list is missing VPC endpoints for:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      163[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **EventBridge** (`com.amazonaws.{region}.events`): Lambda needs to interact with EventBridge for orchestration
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      164[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Glue** (`com.amazonaws.{region}.glue`): If Glue jobs run in the VPC (recommended for PHI processing), they need S3 and CloudWatch endpoints at minimum
