[0m[49m[38;5;9m-  74     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m **Finding:** The recipe states 2-5 second end-to-end scoring latency for the real-time path. Lambda in VPC with cold starts, plus a SageMaker endpoint invocation, plus DynamoDB reads/writes, makes 2 seconds optimistic. VPC-attached Lambda cold starts alone can be 5-10 seconds.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      167[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Without these endpoints, traffic routes through NAT Gateway, which works but adds cost and creates an egress path that should be documented.
