[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      181[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Fix:** Minor: add a note in the cost estimate that cross-AZ data transfer between Kinesis and Lambda adds ~$0.01/GB. For most intervention timing workloads (small event payloads, moderate throughput), this is negligible ($5-20/month). But for systems ingesting high-frequency vitals data, it could be material.
